<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
     <div rend="parallel">
     <p xml:id="Aink212-kilavi"> varaivetir koḷḷār tama ravaṇ maṟuttavaḻit tōḻi cevilik kaṟattoṭu niṉṟatu. </p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> The confidante standing up with virtue to the foster-mother when those who do not accept the marriage (i.e., her people) refused [to give] her to [his] people.  </p>
      </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink212">
<l>cānta maratta pūḻi leḻupukai</l>
<l>kūṭṭuvirai kamaḻu nāṭa</l>
<l>ṉaṟavaṟ kevaṉō nāmakal vaṉṉāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">

<l>Why [on earth] did we leave the dutiful one, </l>
<l rend="indent">he from the land where the mingled aroma </l>
<l rend="indent">of rising smoke from Eaglewood among  Sandalwood trees, </l>
<l>emits fragrance? </l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
